OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FBank Holiday Monday will be dry
OL,6,Fand settled with high pressure
OL,7,Fdominating, giving almost unbroken
OL,8,Fsunshine throughout the day. It will
OL,9,Fbecome hot in the light winds, with
OL,10,Fafternoon temperatures not far off
OL,11,Fbreaking records for May.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FThe fine weather will
OL,14,Fcontinue overnight. There will be lots
OL,15,Fof sunshine to end the day. Patchy
OL,16,Fcloud will develop overnight, but
OL,17,Fremaining dry. Quite a warm night too.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
