OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FAnother mainly dry, often
OL,6,Fsunny and hot day is on the cards on
OL,7,FTuesday. However, some patchy cloud is
OL,8,Fpossible, and an isolated thundery
OL,9,Fshower cannot be ruled out later.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FThe
OL,12,Fweather will stay warm through the
OL,13,Fweek, though cooler than recently.
OL,14,FThere will be some sunshine at times,
OL,15,Fthough a chance of a few showers,
OL,16,Fwhich could turn thundery.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
